<doc id="932825" wikidata="Q5570509" url="?curid=932825" title="Global Neighborhood Watch">
<text>&quot;Global Neighborhood Watch&quot; is an article by Neal Stephenson that appeared in &quot;Wired Magazine&quot; in 1998. In it he proposes a specific plan for using information technology to fight crime. According to Stephenson, he is no longer pursuing the idea.

