*John Brunious
*Raymond Burke
*Chuck Carbo
*Ken Colyer
*Lionel Ferbos
*Pete Fountain
*George Lewis
*Freddie Lonzo
*Teddy Riley
*Kid Sheik
*Michael White
*Young Tuxedo Brass Band
*Chester Zardis

